Oh gosh, that couldn't have happened at a worse time....
{{sticker:zombie-brand-facepalm}} 

Basically, your client realized that some of the files were damaged, so it reverted to a previous stable patch so that it could redownload those files (hopefully without any issues this time). Your best bet would be to let the patcher update again, but if you want to make doubly sure that everything should run correctly you can grab our [**Hextech Repair Tool**](https://support.riotgames.com/hc/en-us/articles/224826367-Automated-Troubleshooting-Hextech-Repair-Tool) and run a force repatch.
